Possible Themes 

1. Ecosystem:

Clock which animates the ecosystem according to time

Example: Sun rises at 6AM, Animals wake up during 7AM, Birds fly during a specific hour, Sun sets at 7PM, Moon, etc. Position of Sun / Moon changes according to time

2. Daily Routine:

Clock which animates a person's daily routine

Example: Wake up, eat breakfast, go for walk, study, etc. 

3. Optical Illusions Mechanized

Make a mechianized / animated optical illusion which functions in time intervals.

